00:00:17.265 --> 00:00:19.140
easy for developers
to incorporate

11
00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:22.290
speech-to-text capabilities
into their applications.

12
00:00:22.290 --> 00:00:23.910
In this course, I'll highlight

13
00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:25.814
the features of
Amazon Transcribe,

14
00:00:25.814 --> 00:00:27.480
talk a bit about how it works,

15
00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:30.210
and provide a few examples
of common use cases.

